🍉️1.We can alter the table using using following comand.
  --> ALTER TABLE COMPANY ADD  gender char(1);

🍉️2.Droping the column.
  --> alter table company DROP column gender;

🍉️3.Adding the constraints.
  -->alter table company ADD CONSTRAINT  pri PRIMARY KEY(id);


🍉️4.deleting the constraint.
  --> ALOTER TABLE COMPANY DROP CONSTRAINT pri;
